{"tid":627931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又來了！]讀唔成書都搵到錢　地盤雜工日薪多大學生8成","createTime":"2018-04-13T11:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:23:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc27f80d2eaa8cd2903d4c9b59e7e219fc62f63","tid":627931,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"地盤雜工收入高過大學生8成！上述絕非戲言，根據財經事務及庫務局的資料顯示，普通工人及雜工的日薪過去3年不斷增加，由2015年的867.4港元，升至去年1032.6港元，升幅近2成。以一個月工作26日計算，即月入有逾2.68萬港元，較初入職大學生平均月入1.48萬港元，多逾8成。<br />\n<br />\n雖然地盤雜工日薪逾千港元，惟只屬地盤行內的「低薪一族」，難與一眾熟練技工人比較。地盤內最高薪職位非市民熟悉的紮鐵或釘板工人，而是潛水員，日薪達2363港元；其次是紮鐵及釘板工人，日薪分別有2088.3及1994.4港元，如按一個月26工作天計算，3個工種的月入由5.19萬港元至6.14萬港元不等，全部高於政府二級行政主任的頂薪點5.09萬港元。一眾年輕人或可考慮「棄筆從建」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413184316902-0413_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fbkn-20180413184316902-0413_00822_001.html&d=Voc7XZDaq3ERB9ldoR2bIS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9e4dd79f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bkn-20180413184316902-0413_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6eedd9a4310897bb04116a5b2177207a8b39910","tid":627931,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d156b2478a169b847a003647c0c4a03a98365fc6","tid":627931,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"once per year<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"